  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "While preparing the Witti multi-client testnet, we had Prysm and Lighthouse disagreeing on the correct genesis time.\r\n\r\nThe reason is that LH honors ETH1_FOLLOW_DISTANCE whereas Prysm only starts honoring this _after_ genesis.\r\n\r\nIt should be clarified whether ETH1_FOLLOW_DISTANCE applies to all ETH1 related events or only after the genesis event.\r\n\r\nLighthouse assumed that was the case whereas Prysm points out that this is not clearly defined in the spec.",
